  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/b613dbb2-90a1-47be-9d77-77bbe98582b9_02.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 580px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《美剧天天秀》节目是沪江部落一档模仿类节目，目的在于提升大家的英语口语水平，在轻松看美剧的同时锻炼大家的口语能力。积极参与的童鞋还会得到主持的专业点评哦！</span><a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15632/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/b613dbb2-90a1-47be-9d77-77bbe98582b9_01.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">去沪江部落订阅本节目！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/b613dbb2-90a1-47be-9d77-77bbe98582b9_00.jpg\" style=\"height: 338px; width: 600px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>原录音：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p541859\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>原文：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tChandler: Oh, I think this is the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/episode\" target=\"_blank\">episode</a> of Three's Company where there's some kind of misunderstanding.<br />\n\tPhoebe:...Then I've already seen this one ! (Turns off the TV.)<br />\n\tMonica: (taking a drink from Joey) Are you through with that?<br />\n\tJoey: Yeah, sorry, the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/swallowing\" target=\"_blank\">swallowing</a> slowed me down.<br />\n\tMonica: Whose little ball of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/paper\" target=\"_blank\">paper</a> is this?!<br />\n\tChandler: Oh, uh, that would be mine. See, I wrote a note to myself, and then I realised I didn't need the note, so I balled it up and ... (sees that Monica is glaring at him) ...now I wish I was dead.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>重点词汇发音讲解：&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1. episode<br />\n\t英[ˈɛpɪˌsəʊd] 美[ˈɛpəˌsoʊd]<br />\n\tn. 片段，插曲；（整个事情中的）一个事件；一集</p>\n<p>\n\t2.swallowing<br />\n\t['swɔləuɪŋ]<br />\n\t吞咽，下咽运动</p>\n<p>\n\t3. through with<br />\n\tphr. 完成，结束；了结，断绝<br />\n\tballed it up: 将它揉成纸团</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15632/item/838050/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p><br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p541859/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p541859\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543812/\">纽约地铁温情一幕：让他靠着我睡会吧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543801/\">11.11又来了：光棍们悲剧大盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543538/\">又萌又有爱：7封小朋友写的情书</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p431046/\">告别单身从朋友下手：7招将朋友变成恋人！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488758/\">一个月搞定新题型 强化直达四六级！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543387/\">8个浪费钱的小习惯 你为啥这么穷！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543685/\">解读四六级听力新题型备考方案</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543887/\">关于咖啡的英语：速溶咖啡怎么说？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p542313/\">关于笑声你可能不知道的9个好处</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\